sentences.sentence: Richful optoelectronic products have become more and more well-known enterprises at home and abroad partners.
sentences.translation: 瑞丰光电产品已成为国内外越来越多知名企业的合作伙伴。

sentences.sentence: This paper is aimed to research and realize a new-type optoelectronic current transformer to replace traditional ct.
sentences.translation: 本文旨在研究和实现一种新型的光电式电流互感器，以取代传统CT。
